Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.96,0:22:50.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\b1\bord4\3c&H000000&\3a&H32&\fad(0,300)\pos(1650,840)}Nụ cười
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kì tới, "Nụ cười".
